1.设置jenkins权限
#修改权限为root用户
vi /etc/sysconfig/jenkins
JENKINS_USER="root"
#修改目录权限
chown -R root:root /var/lib/jenkins
chown -R root:root /var/cache/jenkins
chown -R root:root /var/log/jenkins

2.全局工具配置
系统管理->全局工具配置：配置JDK、GIT、Allure Commandline等插件

3.allure
#构建->执行shell
cd /jimmy/git/PytestAllure
/usr/local/python3/bin/pytest --alluredir ${WORKSPACE}/result

#构建后操作->Allure Report:
Results Path：result，需与上面的${WORKSPACE}后路径一致
JDK：改为全局设置的版本